    "problemStatement": "** Short Answer - 2.5 marks.**\n\nWrite a program to take two numbers as input and print their difference if the first number is greater than the second number otherwiseotherwiseotherwise print their sum.\n\n\nInput Format\nFirst line will contain two numbers, (N1)( N1 )(N1) and (N2),( N2 ),(N2), separated by a space.\n\n\n\nOutput Format\nOutput a single line containing the difference of 2 numbers (N1\u2212N2)(N1 - N2)(N1\u2212N2) if the first number is greater than the second number otherwise output their sum (N1+N2)(N1 + N2)(N1+N2).",
    "constraints": [
